@startuml aggregate_boundary
!include ../theme.iuml

title Hranice agregátu: Order vs. Customer

package "Aggregate: Order" as OrderAgg {
  class "<<root>>\nOrder" as OrderRoot {
    +OrderId id
    +CustomerId customerId
    +OrderStatus status
    +int version
    --
    +place(items)
    +pay()
    +ship()
    +cancel()
  }

  class "<<entity>>\nOrderItem" as OrderItem {
    +OrderItemId id
    +ProductId productId
    +int quantity
    +Money unitPrice
  }

  class "<<value object>>\nMoney" as Money {
    +int amount
    +Currency currency
  }

  class "<<value object>>\nShippingAddress" as ShippingAddress {
    +string street
    +string city
    +string zip
    +CountryCode country
  }

  OrderRoot *-- OrderItem : obsahuje 1..n
  OrderRoot *-- ShippingAddress : má
  OrderItem *-- Money : má
}

package "Aggregate: Customer" as CustomerAgg {
  class "<<root>>\nCustomer" as CustomerRoot {
    +CustomerId id
    +EmailAddress email
    +int version
  }
}

OrderRoot ..> CustomerRoot : odkaz pouze\npřes CustomerId\n(NE objektová reference)

note right of OrderAgg
  Transakční hranice =
  hranice agregátu.
  Doctrine flush()
  ukládá pouze tento agregát.
end note

note bottom of CustomerAgg
  Změna v Customer
  je oddělená transakce
  (eventual consistency
  přes doménový event).
end note

@enduml
